=== Optimised ammunition ===
GIAT and its successor companies have developed and produced {{cvt|155|mm}} rounds designed to maximise the range of the CAESAR, such as the '''LU 211''',<ref name="edr magazine">{{cite web |url=https://www.edrmagazine.eu/increasing-effectiveness-and-range-the-new-lu-220-he-155-mm-munition-by-nexter-arrowtech |title=Increasing effectiveness and range: the new LU 220 HE 155 mm munition by Nexter Arrowtech |last=Valpolini |first=Paolo |date=20 May 2022 |website=European Defence Review |publisher=European Defence Publishing SAS |access-date=22 July 2024}}</ref> which is manufactured at ''Les Forges de [[Tarbes]]'',<ref name="lepafp">{{cite news |author=<!--Not stated--> |date=7 April 2023 |title=Avec la guerre en Ukraine, les besoins en obus relancent une usine d'armement à Tarbes |trans-title=With the war in Ukraine, the need for shells revives an arms factory in Tarbes |url= https://www.leparisien.fr/hautes-pyrenees-65/video-avec-la-guerre-en-ukraine-les-besoins-en-obus-relancent-une-usine-darmement-a-tarbes-07-04-2023-YTANZOSJ6ZGUZNGVH7NV7IRDME.php |language=fr |work=[[Le Parisien]] |location= Paris |publisher=[[LVMH]] |access-date=20 June 2024}}</ref> within the confines of the town arsenal.<ref name="latrib">{{cite news |last1=Déjean |first1=Jean-Philippe |date=28 May 2021 |title=Europlasma va prendre le contrôle de Tarbes Industry pour sécuriser sa croissance |trans-title=Europlasma will take control of Tarbes Industry to secure its growth |url= https://objectifaquitaine.latribune.fr/business/industrie/2021-05-28/europlasma-va-prendre-le-controle-de-tarbes-industry-pour-securiser-sa-croissance-885550.html |language=fr |work=[[La Tribune]] |location=Paris |access-date=20 June 2024}}</ref> The forge was privatised in November 2021 by a French firm which had recently been recapitalised by €100 million.<ref name=latrib/><ref name="tribord">{{cite news |last1=Déjean |first1=Jean-Philippe |date=30 April 2021 |title=Europlasma met en action la deuxième phase de son plan de développement |trans-title=Europlasma implements the second phase of its development plan |url=https://objectifaquitaine.latribune.fr/innovation/2021-04-30/europlasma-met-en-action-la-deuxieme-phase-de-son-plan-de-developpement-883699.html |language=fr |work=La Tribune |location= Paris |access-date=20 June 2024}}</ref> In 2020, the [[Ministre des armées|Minister of the Armed Forces]] signed a contract worth €25 million for the plant to supply shells to the French Army for the decade. The privatisation furnished €9 million each year for the 2021–2024 period. In autumn 2021, the firm supplied an extra €2 million to modernise the plant, which also produces 120&nbsp;mm ammunition for the [[Leclerc tank]].<ref name="fop">{{cite web |url=https://www.forcesoperations.com/amp/un-nouveau-cap-pour-les-forges-de-tarbes/ |title=Un nouveau cap pour les Forges de Tarbes |last=Gain |first=Nathan |date=12 October 2021 |website=Forces Operations Blog |language=fr |trans-title=A new direction for the Tarbes forges |access-date=20 June 2024}}</ref>

