**CAESAR coalition for Ukraine: At the launch, on 18 January 2024, of the Artillery Coalition led by France and the United States to support the Ukrainian war effort.<ref>{{Cite press release |author=<!--Not stated--> |date=25 January 2024 |title=Artillery coalition 'helping Ukraine built its future artillery' |url=https://www.defense.gouv.fr/en/news/artillery-coalition-helping-ukraine-built-its-future-artillery |access-date=19 July 2024 |publisher=[[Ministry of Armed Forces (France)|Ministry of Armed Forces]]}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last=Pietralunga |first=Cédric |date=18 January 2024 |title=France and US head coalition to strengthen Ukraine's artillery |url=https://www.lemonde.fr/en/international/article/2024/01/18/france-and-us-take-head-of-coalition-to-strengthen-ukraine-s-artillery_6443346_4.html |access-date=22 June 2024 |work=[[Le Monde]] |publisher=[[Groupe Le Monde]] |location=Paris}}</ref> The intent is to produce 78 units for Ukraine in 2024.<ref>{{cite news |last=Salaün |first=Tangi |date=18 January 2024 |editor-last=Hénault |editor-first=Blandine |title=La France va produire 78 canons Caesar pour l'Ukraine en 2024-Lecornu |url=https://www.challenges.fr/top-news/la-france-va-produire-78-canons-caesar-pour-l-ukraine-en-2024-lecornu_880459 |access-date=22 June 2024 |language=fr |website=[[Challenges (magazine)|Challenges]].fr |agency= Reuters}}</ref>
